{
  "page": "Feature quote/219",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Was that <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the giants\">their king</a>?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a><br />“<a href=\"/index.php/Giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Giant\">Giants</a> have no kings, no more'n <a href=\"/index.php/Mammoth\" title=\"Mammoth\">mammoths</a> do, nor <a href=\"/index.php/Snow_bear\" title=\"Snow bear\">snow bears</a>, nor the great whales o' the grey sea. That was <a href=\"/index.php/Mag_Mar_Tun_Doh_Weg\" title=\"Mag Mar Tun Doh Weg\">Mag Mar Tun Doh Weg</a>. Mag the Mighty. You can kneel to him if you like, he won't mind. I know your <a href=\"/index.php/Kneeler\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kneeler\">kneeler</a>'s knees must be itching, for want of some king to bend to. Watch out he don't step on you, though. Giants have bad eyes, and might be he wouldn't see <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">some little crow</a> all the way down there by his feet.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund Giantsbane</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Jon II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404155015\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 se